15:15.373 --> 15:18.209
-How long have you lived next door to me?
-Ten years.

15:18.292 --> 15:19.752
Great. Thank you.

15:19.836 --> 15:22.463
- Are you ready?
- Yep.

15:24.715 --> 15:27.677
Yoo-hoo!

15:27.760 --> 15:30.930
-Hi, neighbor.
-Hi.

15:31.013 --> 15:32.765
