16:16.851 --> 16:18.936
-I promise I'll be right there. Bye.
-Can I call you back?

16:19.061 --> 16:21.939
Look, just let me call you back.
Okay. Okay, bye.

16:22.023 --> 16:24.192
-What's going on?
-Penny scraped her knee trick-or-treating,

16:24.275 --> 16:26.235
-and she's crying.
-Oh, no! Is she okay?

16:26.319 --> 16:27.528
I think she's fine
but she's freaking out.

16:27.612 --> 16:28.654
Is it really bad?

16:28.738 --> 16:30.865
I don't think it's really bad,
but she, like, wants me to come,

16:30.948 --> 16:32.617
and Tom doesn't want to deal with it,
so I'm gonna--

16:32.700 --> 16:33.993
-Oh, shit.
-That sounds really important.

16:34.076 --> 16:35.495
Why don't you call Trevin back
and I'll...

16:35.578 --> 16:36.621
